Package: capstoneproject
Type: Package
Title: Package uses the U.S. National Oceanographic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA) data to provide
        useful functions and methods on earthquakes all over the world
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Federico Sensi <federico.sensi@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Federico Sensi <federico.sensi@gmail.com>
Description: Package uses the U.S. National Oceanographic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA) data to provide
    useful functions and methods on earthquakes all over the world.
    To simplify the usage of NOAA data the package provides a set of visualization functions that allow user to immediately
    catch the main information on eartquakes based on their magnitude, intensity and geographical location.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
